  <p>The Council of General Synod approved the appointment of the following members to sessional committees for General Synod 2007, with authority for the Prolocutor in consultation with the General Secretary, to fill any vacancies that may occur.</p>
  <p><strong>Agenda Committee</strong>: shall consist of not more than eight members to be drawn from the members of the General Synod. It shall be the responsibility of the committee to prepare and publish the agenda for each day of the session.</p>
